Package: libkgapi-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: kdepimlibs5-dev, libkgapi2-2 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: libkgapi2-2-dev (<< 2.1.1)
Replaces: libkgapi2-2-dev (<< 2.1.1)
Description: Google API library for KDE -- development files
 LibKGAPI (previously called LibKGoogle) is a C++ library that implements APIs
 for various Google services.
 .
 This package contains development files for building software that uses
 the LibKGAPI library.

Package: libkgapi2-2
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Google API library for KDE
 LibKGAPI (previously called LibKGoogle) is a C++ library that implements APIs
 for various Google services.
 .
 This package contains the LibKGAPI library for API version 2 which is needed
 for KDE >= 4.11.

